Iqtarabati a*l*ss_a_AAatu wa*i*nshaqqa alqamar*u*
Wa-in yaraw _a_yatan yuAAri_d_oo wayaqooloo si_h_run mustamirr*un*
Waka_thth_aboo wa*i*ttabaAAoo ahw_a_ahum wakullu amrin mustaqirr*un*
Walaqad j_a_ahum mina al-anb_a_-i m_a_ feehi muzdajar*un*
_H_ikmatun b_a_lighatun fam_a_ tughnee a*l*nnu_th_ur*u*
Fatawalla AAanhum yawma yadAAu a*l*dd_a_AAi il_a_ shay-in nukur*in*
KhushshaAAan ab_sa_ruhum yakhrujoona mina al-ajd_a_thi kaannahum jar_a_dun muntashir*un*
Muh_t_iAAeena il_a_ a*l*dd_a_AAi yaqoolu alk_a_firoona h_atha_ yawmun AAasir*un*
Ka_thth_abat qablahum qawmu noo_h_in faka_thth_aboo AAabdan_a_ waq_a_loo majnoonun wa*i*zdujir*a*
FadaAA_a_ rabbahu annee maghloobun fa*i*nta_s_ir
Fafata_h_n_a_ abw_a_ba a*l*ssam_a_-i bim_a_-in munhamir*in*
Wafajjarn_a_ al-ar_d_a AAuyoonan fa*i*ltaq_a_ alm_a_o AAal_a_ amrin qad qudir*a*
Wa_h_amaln_a_hu AAal_a_ _tha_ti alw_ah_in wadusur*in*
Tajree bi-aAAyunin_a_ jaz_a_an liman k_a_na kufir*a*
Walaqad tarakn_a_h_a_ _a_yatan fahal min muddakir*in*
Fakayfa k_a_na AAa_tha_bee wanu_th_ur*i*
Walaqad yassarn_a_ alqur-_a_na li*l*_thth_ikri fahal min muddakir*in*
Ka_thth_abat AA_a_dun fakayfa k_a_na AAa_tha_bee wanu_th_ur*i*
Inn_a_ arsaln_a_ AAalayhim ree_h_an _s_ar_s_aran fee yawmi na_h_sin mustamirr*in*
TanziAAu a*l*nn_a_sa kaannahum aAAj_a_zu nakhlin munqaAAir*in*
Fakayfa k_a_na AAa_tha_bee wanu_th_ur*i*
Walaqad yassarn_a_ alqur-_a_na li*l*_thth_ikri fahal min muddakir*in*
Ka_thth_abat thamoodu bi*al*nnu_th_ur*i*
Faq_a_loo abasharan minn_a_ w_ah_idan nattabiAAuhu inn_a_ i_th_an lafee _d_al_a_lin wasuAAur*in*
Aolqiya a*l*_thth_ikru AAalayhi min baynin_a_ bal huwa ka_ththa_bun ashir*un*
SayaAAlamoona ghadan mani alka_ththa_bu al-ashir*u*
Inn_a_ mursiloo a*l*nn_a_qati fitnatan lahum fa*i*rtaqibhum wa*i*_st_abir
Wanabbi\hum anna alm_a_a qismatun baynahum kullu shirbin mu_h_ta_d_ar*un*
Fan_a_daw _sah_ibahum fataAA_ata_ faAAaqar*a*
Fakayfa k_a_na AAa_tha_bee wanu_th_ur*i*
Inn_a_ arsaln_a_ AAalayhim _s_ay_h_atan w_ah_idatan fak_a_noo kahasheemi almu_h_ta\_th_\ir*i*
Walaqad yassarn_a_ alqur-_a_na li*l*_thth_ikri fahal min muddakir*in*
Ka_thth_abat qawmu loo_t_in bi*al*nnu_th_ur*i*
Inn_a_ arsaln_a_ AAalayhim _has_iban ill_a_ _a_la loo_t_in najjayn_a_hum bisa_h_ar*in*
NiAAmatan min AAindin_a_ ka_tha_lika najzee man shakar*a*
Walaqad an_th_arahum ba_t_shatan_a_ fatam_a_raw bi*al*nnu_th_ur*i*
Walaqad r_a_wadoohu AAan _d_ayfihi fa_t_amasn_a_ aAAyunahum fa_th_ooqoo AAa_tha_bee wanu_th_ur*i*
Walaqad _s_abba_h_ahum bukratan AAa_tha_bun mustaqirr*un*
Fa_th_ooqoo AAa_tha_bee wanu_th_ur*i*
Walaqad yassarn_a_ alqur-_a_na li*l*_thth_ikri fahal min muddakir*in*
Walaqad j_a_a _a_la firAAawna a*l*nnu_th_ur*u*
Ka_thth_aboo bi-_a_y_a_tin_a_ kullih_a_ faakha_th_n_a_hum akh_th_a AAazeezin muqtadir*in*
Akuff_a_rukum khayrun min ol_a_-ikum am lakum bar_a_atun fee a*l*zzubur*i*
Am yaqooloona na_h_nu jameeAAun munta_s_ir*un*
Sayuhzamu aljamAAu wayuwalloona a*l*ddubur*a*
Bali a*l*ss_a_AAatu mawAAiduhum wa*al*ss_a_AAatu adh_a_ waamar*ru*
Inna almujrimeena fee _d_al_a_lin wasuAAur*in*
Yawma yus_h_aboona fee a*l*nn_a_ri AAal_a_ wujoohihim _th_ooqoo massa saqar*a*
Inn_a_ kulla shay-in khalaqn_a_hu biqadar*in*
Wam_a_ amrun_a_ ill_a_ w_ah_idatun kalam_h_in bi*a*lba_s_ar*i*
Walaqad ahlakn_a_ ashy_a_AAakum fahal min muddakir*in*
Wakullu shay-in faAAaloohu fee a*l*zzubur*i*
Wakullu _s_agheerin wakabeerin musta_t_ar*un*
Inna almuttaqeena fee jann_a_tin wanahar*in*
Fee maqAAadi _s_idqin AAinda maleekin muqtadir*in*
